{
  "stem": "22447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we was-- after the fighting in-- in Haarlem died down, we got pulled back from Nijmegen, and we were static.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In a little place called Zon-- Z-O-N-- a little place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We looked after the bridges, the Bailey bridges.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And word come around, there's two tickets-- I think it was two tickets to go to Brussels for Christmas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody wanted to go because they are all friendly in the villages there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had their girlfriends there, and they were-- so they were invited out for Christmas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I said, all right, I'll go to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first thing you do, you look for a shul.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had the folder, certain army welfare services.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've got the Paris one, but the Brussels ones are lost, I haven't got it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've got the Paris one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked up the-- and it gave you a map with places of worship were-- Church of England, Catholic, synagogues-- I thought, there's a shul here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was like the main shul of Brussels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the doors were open, the lights were on, and I went in, and no one there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a big lectern, as you go in, with a visitors book, you should sign it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the Americans signed it, but what they shouldn't have done, they put Private First Class and their regiment and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which they shouldn't have done, because someone can see what regiment, and it's bad intelligence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just put your name, rank and number.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went in, all the lights were on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked around, I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't a scratch on the paintwork.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in a beautiful condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I called out, hello, hello, anyone there?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
